item.description: EFT is a remarkable new self-healing technique that uses your body's natural stress-reduction points to produce rapid change. Stimulation of these points by touching or tapping has been scientifically demonstrated to quickly reduce anxiety, depression, and phobias. EFT also has the potential to improve your mood, boost your vitality, and dramatically improve your performance in the fields of work, money, and sports. Please join us on Monday night August 8, 2011 at 6:00pm as we learn more about EFT and how it can help us on a day to day basis. Program will be presented by Barb Tremlett
item.how_to_find_us: Murphy Drive is located off of Northeastern Blvd, in Nashua, NH
